,"msg":"攬炒咁死先最靚"},{"pid":"2ee17a691ef65c160b1662f229fdad7c33134775","tid":1479151,"uid":13330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:50:40.000Z","msg":"死咗就一定樣衰㗎喇<br />\n咪理條仆街<br />\n同bb好好過生活啦"},{"pid":"d17d8ea85f4b3b267bb72f1c6e8b45ae58f2efe0","tid":1479151,"uid":247032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aa214a00b080a7535c4af80eb049811a0e469b9","tid":1479151,"uid":27452,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T19:16:23.000Z","msg":"睇住香港人咁贏落去 老住咁死最爽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:51:41.000Z","msg":"入黎就係想講呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3604288a7e293c0d59ea8a34aa00f44e547476","tid":1479151,"uid":44255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"要死都睇下林鄭點死先<br />\n同埋，去過白事都知，活著最靚"},{"pid":"2684927c9d2994cde7ecee9823e721d7ebf5afac","tid":1479151,"uid":114449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T03:02:25.000Z","msg":"認真 燒炭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過傻仔先咁做 香港一定贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82b510f6098176395d1bde7efadd979e644bd69","tid":1479151,"uid":254275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T03:09:12.000Z","msg":"當你年老要離開的時候，全個房間都係你最愛的人，你就會以最靚的笑容迎接死亡"}]}